{"tid":1350452,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[深藍][代人開po]銅鑼灣老闆話何君堯講得好岩喎","createTime":"2019-07-22T12:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T14:19:23.000Z","uid":156375,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1632d86625c82444d5e4995f03fe43d0ef82b0dc","tid":1350452,"uid":156375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:56:05.000Z","msg":"【代人開post既，岩岩收工就趕住幫佢開post】<br />\n今日食lunch幫襯越色牛肉粉餐廳<br />\n咁岩同班同事一齊討論琴晚睇完真係訓唔著，點解班仆街可以打大肚婆咁<br />\n間嘢老細坐我地隔離枱聽到我地講嘢<br />\n之後係隔離大聲話何君堯講得好岩，話元朗班人咁夜出街抵俾人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個廢青係垃圾戴口罩遊行同拆西環辦事處敢做唔敢認<br />\n 衰過班賊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家諗返起都肚痛，話唔定要睇急症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩返cwb既兄弟小心d呢間嘢，特別係消防同衛生果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-%E8%B6%8A%E8%89%B2%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E7%B2%89%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3-%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3-%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E8%8F%9C-r467705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Fr-%25E8%25B6%258A%25E8%2589%25B2%25E7%2589%259B%25E8%2582%2589%25E7%25B2%2589%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3-%25E9%258A%2585%25E9%2591%25BC%25E7%2581%25A3-%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%258D%2597%25E8%258F%259C-r467705&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=7689813c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-%E8%B6%8A%E8%89%B2%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E7%B2%89%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3-%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3-%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E8%8F%9C-r467705</a><br />\n<br />\n食完先feel到碗嘢唔係幾乾淨咁...聽日都唔知點算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t1hMfT5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft1hMfT5.jpg&h=717acb66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac919388be567a6283f5d63de845536b66b39709","tid":1350452,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:56:21.0